</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Indica se um nó é um descendente de um dado nó.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">node.contains( otherNode )\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>node</code> é o nó que está sendo comparado.</li>\n <li><code>otherNode</code> é o nó contra o qual está sendo comparado.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>O valor de retorno é <code>true</code> se <code>otherNode</code> é um descendente de um nó ou o próprio nó. Caso contrário o valor de retorno é <code>false</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Esta função verifica se um elemento está no corpo da página. As <code>contains</code> is inclusive and determining if the body contains itself isn't the intention of <code>isInPage</code> this case explicitly returns <code>false</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">isInPage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">node</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">contains</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>node</code> é o nó <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span class=\"hps\">que</span> <span class=\"hps\">desejamos verificar</span> se está <span class=\"hps\">no</span>&nbsp;</span><code>&lt;body&gt;</code>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/9\" title=\"Released on 2011-12-20.\">9.0</a> (9.0)</td>\n   <td>5.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>5.2.2 <a href=\"https://code.google.com/p/doctype-mirror/wiki/ArticleNodeContains\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">[1]</a><a href=\"https://github.com/okfn/annotator/blob/master/src/range.coffee#L366\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">[2]</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>9.0 (9.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/domcore/#dom-node-contains\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 4: contains</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Ver também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>Node.hasChildNodes</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"summary"},{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"},{"text":"Ver também","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Indica se um nó é um descendente de um dado nó.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.contains()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.contains()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Node.contains","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.contains()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.contains()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Node.contains","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.contains","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/node/contains","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/node/contains/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node/contains","title":"Node.contains"}],"pageTitle":"Node.contains - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}